Package: myIO
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Data Visualizations Using 'd3.js'
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Ryan", "Morton", email = "morton@myma.us",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Ryan Morton [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Ryan Morton <morton@myma.us>
Description: Create interactive data visualizations powered by 'd3.js' directly
    from R. Provides a layered grammar for bindings composition, supporting
    bar charts, line charts, scatter plots, histograms, treemaps, gauges,
    hexbin plots, heatmaps, candlestick charts, waterfall charts, sankey
    diagrams, boxplots, violin plots, and ridgeline plots. Includes
    transform-driven derived layers, composite chart expansion, tooltips,
    responsive sizing, and 'Shiny' integration.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://mortonanalytics.github.io/myIO/, https://github.com/mortonanalytics/myIO
BugReports: https://github.com/mortonanalytics/myIO/issues
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Suggests:
  testthat (>= 3.0.0),
